 * Installing on Linux and other platforms

INSTALLING ON LINUX AND OTHER PLATFORMS
=======================================

Download and install Python 2.5 from http://www.python.org/download/

Copy the latest version of BB platform to the place where it will live
(e.g. /opt/bbproject/). Go to this directory and run install.sh script
from the root as follows:

 $ sudo install.py
